  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Simplifier au maximum les expressions complexes suivantes.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>En multipliant numérateur et dénominateur par le conjugué du dénominateur : <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}=\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)(1-i)}{(1+i)(1-i)}=\\frac{10+10 i}{2}=5+5 i\\]</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((1-i)^8\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>On a <span class=\"math inline\">\\((1-i)^2=-2 i\\)</span>. On en déduit : <span class=\"math display\">\\[(1-i)^8=\\left((1-i)^2\\right)^4=(-2 i)^4=2^4 \\cdot i^4=16\\]</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5 &amp; =\\left(\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}+\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &amp;=\\left(\\frac{\\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}{\\cos \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}\\right)^5 \\\\ &amp;=\\left(\\frac{e^{i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}{e^{-i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &amp;=\\left(e^{i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}}\\right)^5=e^{i \\frac{10 \\pi}{3}} \\\\\n            &amp; =e^{-i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}} \\\\ &amp;=\\cos \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right) \\\\\n            &amp; =-\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2} &amp; =\\frac{i}{1^2+2 \\sqrt{2} i+(i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\\\ &amp;=\\frac{i}{1-2+2 \\sqrt{2} i}=\\frac{i}{-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i}\\\\ &amp;=\\frac{i(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)}{(-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i)(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)} \\\\\n            &amp; =\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}-i}{(1+8)} \\\\ &amp;=\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}}{9}-\\frac{i}{9}\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
    }
  ]
}